      <hr><a name="skip_menu"></a><h1>010 - Library of Congress Control Number (NR)</h1>
      <hr>
      <div class="formatname">MARC 21 Authority - Full</div>
      <div class="datename">October 2005</div>
      <hr>
      <table width="100%">
